column5: If you are looking to do some world class Walleye,Bass Trout,Perch,Muskie or Salmon fishing with out breaking the bank you need look no further.We have great accomadations at very reasonable rates in either housekeeping or the american plan. Please come by our web site and look at our facilities and compare our prices.We hope to see you on your next trip.http://sawmill-lodge.com/
